quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  26,181,"Nabii Shuqeybi keenik iyyeh: sinaamah tu-elle keexxan keelá duudusaay, keexó daggoysa mara makkina"
  26,182,Kaadu sinaamah massah yan miidaanay duddalel miidaanisa miidaanissaanam
  26,183,"Kaadu sinaamak-le cakki madaggoysinaay, baaxó mabaysina baaxó umaanet baysa mara tikki itteenih"
  26,184,Kaadu Yallay sin kee siinik naharsi ginoona gineh digaalák meesita
  26,185,"Madyan mari Nabii Shuqeybik :cagalah atu elle baaben marih num kinnito kaak iyyen"
  26,186,"Kaadu Shuqeybow atu ninnah yan seehadaytu akke waytek kalah tu hinnitooy, diggah nanu dirableelak numuk teyna koo nakkale kaak iyyen"
  26,187,Tokkel atu qaraanak digaalá kitiifoonuh nel oobis numma yacee marih num tekkek kaak iyyen
  26,188,Nabii Shuqeybi yi-Rabbi isin umaanek abba haytaanam yaaxigeh keenik iyye
  26,189,"Tokkel kaa dirabboyseeniih, gayrantuy ken silaalisa-le ayróh digaalá ken tibbixeeh ken finqisse, diggah woh kaxxa ayróh digaalá kinni"
  26,190,"Diggah too Nabii Shuqeybi marat tekke digaalát kaskassoowa marah astá tan, kaadu keenik maggo mari yeemene mara makko"
  26,191,Kaadu Nabii Mucammadow diggah ku-Rabbi usuk mayso-li xuwaw-li kinni
  26,192,Diggah A-Qhuraan ginô Rabbih xaquk obsime
  26,193,Jibriiliy amaanat-le kaa oobise
  26,194,Yallih farmoytittey Yallih digaalák sinam meesissak numuk teyna takkemkeh ku sorkocobbaxal kaa (Qhuraan kinnuk) oobise
  26,195,Qarab afay baxxaqqa-let kaa oobise
  26,196,Kaadu diggah ama Qhuraanih cusiyyi naharsi ambiyah kitoobah addal yan
  26,197,"Kaadu ama makki koros atu Yallih farmoyta kinnitooh, Qhuraanay kol oobisne cakki kinnim, israa- iil xayloh qolama woh numma kinnim taaxigem astáh ken maxiqtaa"
  26,198,Kaadu Qhuraan qarab akkewaa maray qajam deqsitak numuk teynal kaa oobisinnoy
  26,199,"Tokkel usuk kaa keenil (makki koros kinnuk) akrayuk yeneeh, kaal yeemene mara akkuk manannon"
  26,200,Tonnaah ama Qhuraanih cinaa kee angoddi umeyniitih yan marih sorkocobbaxittet culusneh
  26,201,Usun kaal (Qhuraan kinnuk) mayaaminan qansarissi ken hayta digaalá ubullu haanam fanah
  26,202,"Eddeluk woo digaalá garcik (hurubbak) keenit tamaate, usun mamut teetik aaxige kalah"
  26,203,"Tokkel nanu natoobeeh, naamineh gide a-digaalák nee maay wadirroysan iyyan"
  26,204,Usun Ni-digaaláh obtimii edde qataatakaanaah raksitaanam
  26,205,Nabiyow yoh warisey qumri keenik eyxerri hayneh maggo liggiditte ken sugusneeh hatkisnek
  26,206,Tohuk lakat kah xagnisimak sugen digaalá keenih temeetek
  26,207,Addunyal qumrii kee niqmatak edde hatkisimak sugeenim maca keenih xiqtaah? rabaanak naharal Yallal gace weenik (tu-keenih maxiqta)
  26,208,Kaadu hebeltô magaalah mara mafinqisinnino Yallih digaalák ken meesissah tan farmoytit keenih rubne nee akke waytek
  26,209,"Keenih (makki koros kinnuk) kassiisiiy garci kalootu, kaadu Nanu keenit abneh nan digaalál daalimiin makkinnino"
  26,210,"Kaadu ama Qhuraan Nabiil sheetoona moobisinna, Jibriil oobisê kal"
  26,211,Kaadu woh ken maceltaay keenih matakkaay maduudan
  26,212,Diggah usun (sheetoona kinnuk) qaraanak Qhuraan ankacsaanamak waasimeenimih sabbatah
  26,213,"Toysa Nabiyow Yallâ luk aka Yalla maqbudin, toysa Yalli digaaleh yan marih num akkettok"
  26,214,Kaadu Nabiyow ku-kedók kol xayih yan mara ni-digaalák meesis
  26,215,"Kaadu Nabiyow moominiinik koo kataate marah Ramma ixxicaay, keenih xabbacow"
  26,216,"Tokkel Nabiyow ku-amri cineenik, toysa diggah anu isin abba haytaanamak bari kinniyo keenik ixxic"
  26,217,Kaadu Nabiyow maysoleeh xuwawleh yan Rabbil kelitaay isi caagid kaal kelis
  26,218,Yallay barti salaatah dubuk soltaah abta waqdi koo yablel kelit
  26,219,"Kaadu salaatah sujuud abaah, rukuuq aba marâ luk abta angoyyi kok Yable Rabbil kelit"
  26,220,Diggah Yalli usuk yaabbi yaaxigi kinni
  26,221,"Sinaamey siinih warsoo?keenik ixxic Nabiyow :sheetoona elle obta mara"
  26,222,Usun elle oobaanam ummaan kaxxa dirablih dambi-li
  26,223,"Sheetoona malaykak ankacissaah taabbem jinnilittel hakuyta, keenik maggo mari dirableelah anuk"
  26,224,"Gadaba makkotteeh, maxqawite mari ken kataata"
  26,225,Nabiyow matablaa! usun diggah yabti daqooruk ummaan daqaaral diraabah giirisaanam ilqaa kee faylat caddok taturak
  26,226,Kaadu diggah usun abewayoonu waanam iyyan
  26,227,"Yallal yeemeneeh meqe tamoomi abbaasiteeh Yalla maggom cuseeh yundullumeeniik gamadal Rasuul kee islaam diinik kalalak koros gadabal yab gacsa mara akke waytek. isi nafsii kee seehada yudlume mari aaxige-le kah gacoonu waan gacim kinni gacim rabaak lakal, diggah usuk uma gacim kinni"